WizardTD

Interface Moveable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Beetle, Gremlin, Worm

    public interface Moveable
    The Moveable interface defines the contract for all entities in the WizardTD game that have the capability to move on the game board. This includes methods for getting and setting the entity's path, position, speed, health, and other related attributes. Implementing this interface ensures that the entity adheres to a consistent set of behaviors associated with movement.
